<para>
  <classname>PinnedNodesDisplay</classname> highlights the nodes
  which are <link linkend="Section-Graphics-PinNodes">pinned</link>
  in a &skel;.  Each pinned node is marked with a dot whose radius is
  given, in screen pixel units, by the <varname>size</varname>
  argument.
</para>
<para>
  A single <classname>PinnedNodesDisplay</classname> is created
  automatically in each <link linkend='Chapter-Graphics'>Graphics
  Window</link> and is not normally visible in the window's layer
  list. To edit its properties, first select <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Graphics_n.Settings.List_All_Layers">List
  All Layers</link> in the graphics window's <menuchoice>
  <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> </menuchoice> menu.
</para>


